                                <li><strong>Use CSS Variables:</strong> Always use <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">var(--color-primary)</code>, <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">var(--color-surface)</code>, etc.</li>
                                <li><strong>Never Hardcode Colors:</strong> Avoid hardcoded hex colors like <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">#3b82f6</code> or <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">bg-blue-500</code></li>
