                                <li><strong>Use Theme-Aware Classes:</strong> Prefer <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">theme-card</code>, <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-3);">theme-button</code> utility classes when available</li>
